    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, looking and driving exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep showroom shine, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect; every component has been meticulously maintained, and it comes with a complete service history. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer who wants a like-new vehicle without the new-car price tag.",
